data.description: You don't want to miss this one! Beautiful 3 bed 2 bath brick home on a dead end street. 1200 sqft shop built in 2022. 500 sqft of the shop is heated and cooled. Large area outback perfect for entertaining. Immaculate home with lots of upgrades! Call or text me today to see it!
